node.text: My new AMG Beast #gle63scoupe 🏎💥💥 Twin turbo V8 AMG monster with 634 bhp and 0-60mph in 3.7 seconds. Not bad for such a big sized luxury SUV! #amg Thanks to @thewrapsanctuary for the customisations on the car and @supercar_concierge @wefitanytracker for fitting the security devices.
